'''Domain Cha''' was a [[Domain]] among the [[Warrior caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] and great rivals of [[Domain Kraal]]. Notable members of this domain included [[Wyrpuuk Cha]], as well as his aide, [[Kadlah Cha]]. No members of Domain Cha were present when the ''[[Lusankya/Legends|Lusankya]]'' [[Battle of Borleias (Yuuzhan Vong War; Second)|destroyed]] Domain Cha's military fleet.

